extracted_info.high entropy alloy formula: Al 20 Cr 10 Nb 15 Ti 20 V 25 Zr 10
extracted_info.microstructure: Composite-like hypoeutectic microstructure comprised of a primary B2 phase and a harder eutectic mixture consisting of a C14 Laves and the B2 phases
extracted_info.processing method: Vacuum arc melting, annealed at 1200 °C for 24 h
extracted_info.hardness: As-cast B2 phase: 665 ± 20 HV, Eutectic C14 Laves + B2: 820 ± 30 HV, Annealed B2 phase: 320 ± 25 HV, C14 Laves phase: 460 ± 40 HV, Zr5Al3-type phase: 600 ± 50 HV
